I am proud to be recognized again as the #1 agent in Miami per the MLS for 2022. 

In a year marked by both extraordinary shifts in the marketplace and the founding of our new brokerage @officialpartners our accomplishment is all the more special and meaningful to The @alexanderteam 

This milestone validates three observations I’ve made in more than a decade operating at the highest level:

1. Staying at the top is much more challenging than the climb.

2. A traditional brokerage firm is not the determining success factor in this business. 

3. The surest way to excel in any competitive landscape is to surround yourself with the best talent. Period.

Thank you to my team, clients, partners, family and friends for the continued support.

4th year in a row, The Alexander Team has been recognized as the #1 team in the country with well over a billion in sales. Even though I’m over all these rankings and everyone claiming #1 of everything. But felt the need to post as this was our first year as co-founders of @officialpartners 

Many said that without the backing of a legacy firm, our business would somehow suffer however the opposite has been true. With this latest confirmation of the team’s continued strength we hope others will take note that the potential of one’s business is only limited by your imagination. 

We imagined a firm that deeply resonated with our clients, one that would attract the greatest in our industry and one aligned with the markets that matter to both.

As the founding team of the only brokerage specializing in the pinnacle segment of the market, let this accomplishment serve as an example of what is possible.

Thank you to our clients, peers, family, friends and partners for their support which motivates us to continue striving to redefine the industry and what everyone should expect from our profession.
